###Recipes

### Create Recipe

POST {{baseUrl}}/recipes
content-type: application/json

{
    "name": "Bolo de Chocolate",
    "description": "Delicioso bolo de chocolate",
    "price": 25.50,
    "category": "Bolos"
}

### Get Recipes

GET {{baseUrl}}/recipes

###Orders

### Create Order

POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
content-type: application/json

{
    "customerName": "João Silva",
    "customerPhone": "(11) 99999-9999",
    "items": [
        {
            "recipeId": "recipe-id-here",
            "quantity": 2
        }
    ]
}

### Get Orders

GET {{baseUrl}}/orders

### Get Order by ID

GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/order-id-here

### Change Order Status

PATCH {{baseUrl}}/orders/order-id-here/status
content-type: application/json

{
    "status": "completed"
}

### Get Total Sales

GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/total

### Get Pending Sales

GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/total/pending

### Get Paid Sales

GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/total/paid

### Get Orders with Pagination

GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/pagination?page=1&limit=10